## Context

Split from 0277 (RDJ-26561 R&R, tracker 0274, remark R1-14): the referee
suggests presenting a citation network drawn from the database "to
demonstrate its potential and/or limitations". The editor explicitly
softened this (ED-02): "I am not asking you to conduct these analyses" —
alternatives include institution/co-author networks or simply expanding the
conclusion (ticket 0278). Whether to add a figure at all is the author's
call, hence needs-human.

If declined, the response letter (0283) cites the editor's own alternative
and points to the 0278 conclusion expansion — a reasoned decline closes this
ticket; R1-14 stays covered.

